metadata.name: The Demon's Gifts
metadata.description:
Have you ever wondered if there are new, clever inventions or things in our world on which you can make a lot of money quickly and easily? No? 
Then listen up. 

Belphegor, aka one of the seven princes of Hell, is the demon that gives you the opportunity to get rich. 
The sixth of ten archidemons, offering cunning inventions that can make you successful and rich, in exchange for souls. 

What is it that the demon Belphegor entices mankind with? 
The promise of quick wealth and the fame and glory associated with it. This monstrous creature possesses mad energy and is aware of the latest technological advances. He lures our fellow creatures into his web, enticing them with the opportunity to invent something or make an important discovery.

Now you know that all these hobbies and hobbies that bring a lot of money into our world did not arise by accident. And who contributed to it.
Be careful and be wary of the gifts of Belphegor... sometimes things may not turn out as well as they seem.
